<plot>The tables are turned on Sam, a hapless burglar, when he is caught in the act of robbing a house. Vanessa, his young assailant with his gun in her hands, proposes they be partners in crime. Sam has no other choice but agree to her proposal. But Sam quickly falls under Vanessa's spell. However, Vanessa really has another thought on her mind, one that she has been carrying with her for seven years.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?100255</url></doc>
